Hi Monika! Welcome to NewsBreak! It sounds like you might be experiencing a display issue on the ad management page. Here are a few steps you can try to resolve this:
1. Refresh the page.
2. Clear your browser cache and cookies.
3. Try accessing the page using a different browser or device.
4. Ensure your browser is up-to-date.
If these steps don't work, please email adsupport@newsbreak.com with details about your issue, including screenshots if possible, and they will assist you further.
